Fillers
--------------------

Description:
App intended to help with practicing a speech by showing you a visual representation of all fillers used during a practice run.

Roadmap:
-Phase 1-
* web app with a few preset filler options: um, like, ahh, <long pause>
* requires two people to use: 1 person doing the speech and the other clicking buttons

-Phase 2-
* (GNOME) desktop app with same functionality

-Phase 3-
* new mode with upload pre-recorded speech
* app analyzes audio and finds fillers

-Phase 4-
* real-time audio recording/analysis to find fillers

-Phase 5-
* iPhone app
